entry.title: Yixuan Theme Reimagined - Martial Summit Showdown (Sumes Mix) | Zenless Zone Zero

media:group.media:description:
This is my reimagined version of Yixuan's theme from her character demo "Martial Summit Showdown". It is a little different from my usual covers. I was excited to work on her theme, but the original track in the trailer felt more tailored to the pacing and visuals of the trailer, and rather fragmented unlike like the usual character themes we get (in my opinion). As a result, it didn't have the kind of structure I usually look for when covering a theme.
That said, there were still some musical ideas - melodic fragments, drums, and the distinct instrumentation - that served as the inspiration for this reinterpretation. I was a bit more experimental with this one (especially with the vocal samples and chops xD), and also gave myself a time constraint since I was originally working on a different piece meant to release today.
Anyway, I hope you find some enjoyment in this version of Yixuan's theme, and as always, thank you for listening!
